{"tid":1630472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真+最後警告] 唔好再遊行唱肥媽","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T06:42:20.000Z","uid":218313,"like":197,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6b41163e1266a785ccca128d30efe0a2c91a05","tid":1630472,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"尤其D 高音到仆街既絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知唔知你地一叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呀!!!!!!!~~~~~~~~~~~~</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周圍方圓一公里既人係會突然血壓急升, 心率快左四十<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再左望右望發生咩事<br />\n成條隊拖慢晒<br />\n<br />\n我鄭重警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次再有人遊行唱肥媽<br />\n我真係會衝過去大大力咁有禮貌地叫佢收聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2efccef6d918efa25411fcc6d434c1cb46f5d74","tid":1630472,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d8e79a7a37de78aff9269f4e4ee23b2e40ad070c","tid":1630472,"uid":218313,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"堅認真<br />\n我俾絲打嚇過好撚多次!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acb23bb9ea2cc03b89b6dd3b37424b5f47dd052","tid":1630472,"uid":270111,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"首歌本身又唔好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔明點解咁多人鍾意唱"},{"pid":"3e810fbe9591e7f840d7ab677d1e0ffc30529a14","tid":1630472,"uid":291426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:04.000Z","msg":"我都俾人嚇過好多次"},{"pid":"5157e5bae621ab8f81b236bea57c03fb4ec68d65","tid":1630472,"uid":34516,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"抗爭現場聽到麻煩私了 冇啲咁戇鳩嘅手足"},{"pid":"1431d479bf8e7baef6db89a4cf3afa8407b23abb","tid":1630472,"uid":218313,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0acb23bb9ea2cc03b89b6dd3b37424b5f47dd052","tid":1630472,"uid":270111,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":