單止肥媽<br />\n好多時大隊都會有雜音<br />\n<br />\n反而有需要係檢討<br />\n每次如果係有遊行<br />\n每隔一段距離要有人攞大聲公<br />\n負責幫手帶口號<br />\n匯報最新消息<br />\n同埋可以避免解散軍搞事"},{"pid":"ca43d2d8639eb662410868c58ec28e9ed63f693d","tid":1630472,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5157e5bae621ab8f81b236bea57c03fb4ec68d65","tid":1630472,"uid":34516,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"抗爭現場聽到麻煩私了 冇啲咁戇鳩嘅手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"神獸只對外人出<br />\n<br />\n但呢D 絲打<br />\n你嚇到我, 我會嚇返你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bc7c5542370e1e5e92fac418fae3cd525158ee","tid":1630472,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34c7d15d651dfe3552bf96b7053486212ea92694","tid":1630472,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"推多五次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a500794b99acce113e15fdc4d7cd14b5ad9fcfd2","tid":1630472,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"邊個仆街剪呢首歌出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c1f7dbb512ddc0accd66e0d4576cdbe2b0972d","tid":1630472,"uid":143827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50cafe1ac5623cc68f3a271f9cc7fb7c1519347","tid":1630472,"uid":178716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:07.000Z","msg":"真係會嚇親"},{"pid":"7a8117b15961772a79f4e05ddaa9e0e5da197191","tid":1630472,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"非常同意，需廣傳"},{"pid":"6172a8b0808a6be3a09e07015bebfee1a148ca0d","tid":1630472,"uid":3564,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:06.000Z",